(516,'RIG-IMP-0516',742,'Unknown','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Shoemaker Rigging would provide the labor, equipment, and transportation to relocate and\nreassemble the existing Laser welding cell from Velocys in Plain City, OH to East Grandby, CT.','2025-12-16',10,'Contract',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0.00,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'{\"source_file\":\"Quote.pdf\",\"quote_date_raw\":\"December 16th, 2025\",\"quote_date_iso\":\"2025-12-16\",\"recipient\":{\"name\":null,\"company\":null,\"address\":null,\"email\":null,\"phone\":null},\"work_scope\":null,\"scope_items\":[\"Shoemaker Rigging would provide the labor, equipment, and transportation to relocate and\\nreassemble the existing Laser welding cell from Velocys in Plain City, OH to East Grandby, CT.\",\"Shoemaker Rigging would separate the three main components of the machine and prepare\\nthem for transport.\",\"Shoemaker Rigging would transport the machinery on a step deck Conestoga trailer to protect\\nthe machine from the elements.\",\"The owner would be responsible for the unload and placement of the machinery when it arrives\\nin Connecticut.\"],\"project_conditions\":\"This project is based upon the scope of work listed above. Any work beyond this scope must be approved, in writing, and signed by\\nthe owner or their designated representative. Clear access for cranes, equipment, and labor to all working areas is required. Removal\\nof any obstruction is the responsibility of the owner. It is assumed that all aprons, driveways, hard-surfaced areas, and plant floors are\\nadequate for the necessary loads - static or moving - for all machinery and equipment used on this project. Delays due to non-\\nShoemaker Rigging arranged transportation could incur additional charges.\",\"total_price_raw\":null,\"total_price\":null,\"terms\":\"Full payment prior to machinery shipment. Proposal good for 60 days.\",\"payment_terms\":null,\"proposal_valid_days\":60,\"sender\":{\"name\":null,\"company\":null,\"address\":null,\"phone\":null,\"fax\":null,\"email\":null},\"has_confidentiality_statement\":true,\"raw_text_excerpt\":\"December 16th, 2025\\nGlenn Levesque/ JT Automation\\n17 Connecticut South Drive, East Grandby, CT 06026\\n860-784-1967/ glevesque@JTautomation.com\\nShoemaker Rigging & Transport is pleased to provide this proposal for the following work:\\nWork Scope – Provide the labor, equipment, and transportation to relocate the existing Laser Welding cell\\n• Shoemaker Rigging would provide the labor, equipment, and transportation to relocate and\\nreassemble the existing Laser welding cell from Velocys in Plain City, \"}','Imported from Quote.pdf','2026-04-11 13:32:16','2026-04-11 19:29:58'),
